					</dt>
					<dd class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-1391">
<p>Your scenario of deflationary implosion and hyper-inflationary explosion is very plausible. The interesting question is when the former will transition into the latter, and what are the signs of such impending transition? That would be the last chance to buy cheap gold.<br />
Peter</p>
</div>
					</dd>
